reference "tab:Average-prices-received"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

).
 This may mean that the components that make up the transaction cost are
 modest.
 For instance, distances traveled is short and risk related to trade negligible.
 It also suggests that there is substantial competition between traders.
 The average farmer in the data set indicates that in the seven days before
 the transaction, they were visited by 
